text: Deogracias Biribé Banké (born 27 March 1997) is an Equatorial Guinean footballer who plays as a defensive midfielder for Cano Sport Academy and the Equatorial Guinea national team. ==International career== Biribé made his international debut for Equatorial Guinea on 28 July 2019. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Association football midfielders Category:Equatoguinean footballers Category:Equatorial Guinea international footballers Category:Cano Sport Academy players Category:The Panthers F.C. players Category:Bubi people
